author: andreasmyth
msg: Implementation of configuration (runtime data) provider for configuration files in Spring xml format. This is based on generating a Java Bean for each configurable component, using the component's configuration meta data.
Retrieval of configuration data is restricted to primitive types for now - complex types will be handled later, see tasks for MS3.
Added only the required jars from the Spring distribution to the tools repository (instead of the complete distribution).
Add dependency on systest.compile to target generate.eclipse.workspace.
